# =======================================================================================
# RUNIC SYSTEM CONSTITUTION: IMMUTABLE DESKTOP AGENT DIRECTIVES
# =======================================================================================

- Tech Stack Boundaries: Node.js (v20+), Express, ioredis, pg, ws. Pure backend + vanilla asset bindings.
- Solenoid Architecture: Every operational layer must map cleanly to one of the 14 Pillar Elevators.
- State Chain Rule: All JSON API outputs must append an `x-helix-state-anchor` tracking header.
- Memory Isolation: Enforce absolute zero-copy string cleaning on all incoming cross-chain payloads.
- Safety Canopy: If Redis exceptions clear, drop down instantly into read-through cache fallbacks.
- Coding Standard: No summary comments, no skipped boilerplate, no omitted helper branches, no placeholders.
